1. *Nadam* se da ću uspeti da se usavršim na ovom kursu. (I hope I will be able to perfect myself in this course.)

2. *Nadala* sam se da će sve biti u redu. (I had hoped that everything would be alright.)

3. *Nadanje* je da će sve biti u redu. (The hope is that everything will be alright.)

4. On je imao *nade* da će se situacija poboljšati. (He had hope that the situation would improve.)

5. Ona je bila puna *nade* da će biti srećna. (She was full of hope that she would be happy.)